WEBVTT

00:00:01.531 --> 00:00:03.752
Nikad neću zaboraviti

00:00:03.776 --> 00:00:07.999
svoj prvi susret s 
djevojkom u plavoj uniformi.

00:00:09.577 --> 00:00:12.165
Imala sam osam godina,

00:00:12.189 --> 00:00:15.522
živjela sam u selu s bakom,

00:00:15.546 --> 00:00:18.355
koja me odgajala skupa s drugom djecom.

00:00:19.538 --> 00:00:24.212
Glad je pogodila Zimbabve

00:00:24.236 --> 00:00:27.259
i nismo imali dovoljno hrane.

00:00:28.403 --> 00:00:30.386
Bili smo gladni.